{"tid":810587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男大生打兩晚通宵麻雀猝死 母批學校無監管","createTime":"2018-09-08T05:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T18:37:56.000Z","uid":80516,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2eafee6e37302dc3fdd1cecd55db32a56135882b","tid":810587,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"四川成都19歲大學生王崚西今年7月期末考前，疑因連續兩晚通宵打麻雀，在考試後突然猝死，警方調查後排除涉刑事行爲。惟王母認為兒子之死，是學校無盡到對住校學生的監管責任，周五（7日）帶同親友到學校抗議。學校負責人否認責任，反批王男瞞報病史，雙方一度發生衝突。王母稱，兒子的遺體仍存放在殯儀館未火化，將通過司法途徑維護權益。<br />\n<br />\n王母表示，就讀於四川電影電視學院2017級表演藝術專業的兒子，於7月3日至4日連續兩晚外出，在學校附近的麻雀館打牌，均至翌日清晨才回宿舍，結果於7月5日下午考完試後，突然倒地猝死。她指兒子從年初至7月，共有13晚沒回宿舍，但校方從未向她反映情況，又指事發時校方未及時組織醫療，導致憾事發生。<br />\n<br />\n網上有傳四川電影電視學院近日調派大批保安把持校門，拒絕讓死者親屬入校，據指該校團委書記黃某曾揚言「有辦法收拾在場的學生親屬」，學校保安也出言恐嚇，叫該些親屬小心被打。<br />\n<br />\n四川電影電視學院發聲明回應稱，校方在王男病發後，為他進行約42分鐘的急救，但無法令他恢復呼吸心跳，送院後宣布死亡。警方、法警檢查後判定王男猝死，排除刑事成分，故學校無責。此外，王男曾有患胸部疾病的病史，但他沒有告知學校之餘，也忽略自己身體狀況。聲明又稱，希望通過此事警醒其他學生，應當重視自身健康，呵護生命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hSoijTV22ZoNLwPtCQyroA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ba7fd3d5fee652bf3cee1bdbcfccd097\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhSoijTV22ZoNLwPtCQyroA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fba7fd3d5fee652bf3cee1bdbcfccd097&h=df8640b8&s={SIZE}\" />王男（左圖）事發前約朋友打麻雀的對話紀錄（右圖）。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/photo/bkn-20180908090127790-0908_00952_001_02p.jpg?20180908133926\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180908%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180908090127790-0908_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20180908133926&h=df567365&s={SIZE}\" />網上流傳多名保安在四川電影電視學院校門外把持。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/bkn-20180908090127790-0908_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180908%2Fbkn-20180908090127790-0908_00952_001.html&d=f5gKr6U84mP3KOVxb21sghFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=2281bd5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180908/bkn-20180908090127790-0908_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a202f64a78d3183a75eab66750aa40c24071ce2","tid":810587,"uid":81368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e247fc677f8c6bb642e59574dbb1dad2f18380c","tid":810587,"uid":40968,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"大陸D家長乜都賴人"},{"pid":"1f7bea400d5443fd7087e471555e976632e43aa3","tid":810587,"uid":204549,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:14:51.000Z","msg":"俾地方你住 仲要管埋你個仔 當大學係托兒所？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7835943f98f013329494b9ed956b84cbed2ce457","tid":810587,"uid":63154,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"兩晚通宵坐嚮度，啲血會塞住小腿好危險，啲人話小腿係第二個心臟，一定要定時郁動保持血液流動"},{"pid":"d4652745e008e1354bea2140fabf4d10adba490d","tid":810587,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">條仔好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"15b5e3bdd03bb6fd85de1648e2f7eb852f2dd92d","tid":810587,"uid":24759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"成年人點管？"},{"pid":"13981c36bbf9d5c8863d3c4d0cae27b7bee5cfc9","tid":810587,"uid":70417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/no